    "body": "This cannot be solved without changing the AST: A function type name is not an elementary type name, but only elementary type name, identifiers and literals can be primary expressions. We would have to add a new AST node type, but I'm actually not sure this should be a primary expression. If it is not a primary expression, things get even more complicated.",
